{"tid":865932,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"《FIFA 19》新宣傳片 強姦犯C朗淪為大茄","createTime":"2018-10-17T13:03:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-18T04:45:18.000Z","uid":54373,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"356df34975836722e82c144b9ec8a6615b0791e1","tid":865932,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T13:03:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0ecJgufa9PQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D0ecJgufa9PQ&d=v7SFhVMdNLZxt93nRRuBXDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=ba8cc814\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0ecJgufa9PQ</a><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=v7SFhVMdNLZxt93nRRuBXDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=4d474716\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】祖雲達斯球星 雞姦坦奴朗拿度 在電玩足球遊戲《FIFA 19》的最新廣告片，由之前的主角淪為配角。<br />\n<br />\n祖雲達斯球星 雞姦坦奴朗拿度（Cristiano Ronlado）一直是廣告的主角，以他作封面的足球電子遊戲《FIFA 19》，在最新宣傳中卻僅僅做配角。片段中，以真人姿態出現的是曼城球星奇雲迪布尼和C朗的祖雲達斯隊友保羅戴巴拿，而且兩人是最先出現的，足證兩人在市場有一定地位。 在整個1分30多秒的片段中，C朗也僅佔其中5秒，而且最精彩的片段來自巴黎聖日耳門的尼馬，隨之是戴巴拿射「窩利」的片段。C朗近兩年都是《FIFA》足球遊戲系列的封面主角，這次封面在今夏世界盃決賽周前推出，而新廣告片段最近才面世。 C朗的「失寵」原因，或多或少與捲入9年前的涉嫌性侵案導致形象差有關。"},{"pid":"a093ce7e875b7f2555d7378affaba98c199afedc","tid":865932,"uid":44285,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T13:04:17.000Z","msg":"雞姦坦奴朗拿度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01e3f5acec568905451885bb54a9eac6fa7dd6cc","tid":865932,"uid":83094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T13:04:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dd549ff7522c5443c2779ca565c749880730629b","tid":865932,"uid":54373,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a093ce7e875b7f2555d7378affaba98c199afedc","tid":865932,"uid":44285,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T13:04:17.000Z","msg":"雞姦坦奴朗拿度<img sr